			NAME : Rondo Dunfire<BR>
LEVEL : 10-15<BR>
LOOT : Meat, and &quot;Rondo's Tongue&quot;.<BR>
DESC. : This guy is a bandit residing in Crushbone. You'll find him in the Slaver Mine/Room. He cons yellow to me at Level 8, and I'd say he'd be equal to that if a slaver.<BR>
No Pic.
