			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Behind the wall to the east of the castle is a slave pit where orc slavers and very occasionally taskmasters spawn.  I thought you might want to put this on the map.  There are usually 3 slaves over there and also a little man named Retlon Brenclog who is down in a pit.  He wants a key, but I have yet to figure out which one.  If anyone can help me with this please e-mail me or give me a /tell in game.  I am on the Tunare server.
