		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Unless you want an exercise in frustration, avoid trainer hill<BR>
. It may get better once the shiny braa sheild becomes lore, but<BR>
for now, its a huge jamboree for kill stealers.<BR>
Non-magic types don't have a prayer. You need to be about<BR>
lvl 12 to solo the trainer. Also, people in parties camp up there<BR>
and destroy him constantly. The sheild is about a 1 in 10 chance, and<BR>
sometimes he drops raw-hide.
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
