			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			 I was in groups from two to four camping for the<BR>
Shiny Brass Shield. Non-magic users can kill the <BR>
Trainer without much difficulty, he cond white, <BR>
yellow and red to me, I am a paladin and have <BR>
soloed him several times at level 9 (granted I had to use lay <BR>
hands some of the time) but if you do try to solo <BR>
him try to make sure none of the centurions there <BR>
attack you too, as another four of them attacking <BR>
you when you are trying to kill the trainer can <BR>
be quite a challenge, I found the best tactic for<BR>
that situation is running!<BR>

