		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This is just for all you magic users with pets out there - this zone is a nightmare with a pet.  They get lost in and around the castle/slave area, and get very confused inside the castle.  I saw my pet commit suicide right in front of me in the throne room, in plain of view of me.  Kind of odd, but just be careful.  Not to mention wandering pets can start huge trains, so if you're not very high level and see &quot;Taunting Attacker Master&quot; I suggest you run.
			</font>
	
